-- Bouygues Is Favorite to Win Le Mans-Rennes TGV Contract, La Tribune Says
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-10-13T05:23:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/bouygues-is-favorite-to-win-le-mans-rennes-tgv-contract-la-tribune-says.html
Bouygues SA is the favorite to win
the contract to build a high-speed rail line between Le Mans and
Rennes in the face of competition from Vinci SA and Eiffage SA,
French daily La Tribune reported, without citing anyone.  The project may cost about 3.4 billion euros, according to
the newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  